OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fshould quickly clear. A dry and clear
OL,7,Fnight to follow with the wind easing
OL,8,Flight. Remaining mild in urban areas
OL,9,Fbut much cooler in rural spots.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA dry morning with hazy
OL,12,Fsunshine. The cloud thickens
OL,13,Fthroughout the day with areas seeing
OL,14,Fsome rain by the afternoon. Rain
OL,15,Fbecoming widespread and heavier by the
OL,16,Fevening and overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
